    "Finally, we assessed the impact on learners' revision behavior using a keystroke analysis.",
    "Task Performance.",
    "To assess participants' progress in recipe writing skills, we used each participant's first recipe (i.e., their first submission) as an initial evaluation and their last revised recipe (i.e., their last submission) as a final evaluation.",
    "Specifically, we computed two scores for each recipe: the predicted stars (S y (x)) and the quality score (Q y (x)).",
    "The first score, the predicted stars (S y (x)), was obtained using the model finetuned to predict the recipes' stars (RELEXset-Predictor, see \"Offline Training and Annotation\")."
